    "attributes": {
        "action": "Exempt listening to music and the radio by staff from music licence requirements",
        "additional_details": "I ask for it to be possible to play music or listen to the radio at work without a license needed.\r\n \r\nWe believe it would help improve morale and mental health in multiple sectors.\r\n",
        "background": "Currently businesses must apply for licences to play music or the radio for their employees. We think this requirement should be scrapped to make it easier for people to enjoy music and the radio at work.",
